@baseUrl = https://sap-server:50000/b1s/v1
@session = replace-with-B1SESSION-cookie

# =============================================================================
# UDT: @JCA_DLC_RUN — Resumen de ejecución por corrida
# MVP: CRÍTICA. La aplicación abortará si esta UDT no existe en SAP B1.
# Creación: Ejecutar los requests en orden como usuario B1 Admin.
# Documentación: PRD sección 12.5
# NOTA: El Code de cada registro es el RunId (UUID generado por la app).
#       Un registro con U_Status = RUNNING indica ejecución activa.
#       El LockManager revisa esta tabla al arrancar para prevenir doble ejecución.
# =============================================================================


### PASO 1 — Crear tabla JCA_DLC_RUN
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserTablesMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "JCA_DLC_RUN",
  "TableDescription": "Smart Doc Control - Resumen de ejecucion",
  "TableType": "bott_MasterData"
}


# =============================================================================
# PASO 2 — Crear campos (ejecutar cada request por separado)
# =============================================================================

### Campo U_StartedAt — Fecha y hora de inicio
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_RUN",
  "Name": "StartedAt",
  "Description": "Fecha y hora de inicio",
  "Type": "db_Date"
}

### Campo U_FinishedAt — Fecha y hora de fin
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_RUN",
  "Name": "FinishedAt",
  "Description": "Fecha y hora de fin",
  "Type": "db_Date"
}

### Campo U_Status — Estado de la ejecucion
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_RUN",
  "Name": "Status",
  "Description": "Estado: RUNNING/FINISHED/ERROR/STALE",
  "Type": "db_Alpha",
  "Size": 20
}

### Campo U_CompanyDB — Sociedad SAP B1
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_RUN",
  "Name": "CompanyDB",
  "Description": "Sociedad SAP B1",
  "Type": "db_Alpha",
  "Size": 50
}

### Campo U_Env — Ambiente DEV/TST/PRD
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserFieldsMD
Cookie: B1SESSION={{session}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "TableName": "@JCA_DLC_RUN",
  "Name": "Env",
  "Description": "Ambiente: DEV/TST/PRD",
  "Type": "db_Alpha",
  "Size": 10
}

